{"id":29768808182,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG7lv29g","head_branch":"fix/DHIS2-21860-userrole-usergroup-members-projection","head_sha":"5f88670f24da82f7fb46e43e72618979330c2b8a","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54893,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: avoid full User materialization for userRole/userGroup members projection [DHIS2-21860]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":80615693100,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASxRHbLA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182","pull_requests":[{"id":4093009643,"number":24512,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24512","head":{"ref":"fix/DHIS2-21860-userrole-usergroup-members-projection","sha":"5f88670f24da82f7fb46e43e72618979330c2b8a","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"e4a9688cf130fe90449711315803683fd8851ae5","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-20T18:41:16Z","updated_at":"2026-07-20T18:50:02Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-20T18:41:16Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80615693100","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29768808182/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: avoid full User materialization in LinkService href generation [DHIS2-21856]\n\nLinkService.generateLinks() reflectively calls UserRole.getUsers()/\nUserGroup.getMembers() to stamp href on each member, and runs in the\ncontroller before FieldFilterService ever gets a chance to install the\nDHIS2-21860 summary projection -- so it was still forcing full\nmaterialization of the real, potentially huge member collection just\nto generate hrefs that were then discarded once the summary swap\nhappened later during serialization.\n\n- AbstractFullReadOnlyController gains a beforeLinkGeneration(T, String)\n  hook, called on single-object and list GET before handleLinksAndAccess.\n  Default no-op; zero behavior change for the other ~85 controllers\n  extending this class.\n- UserRoleController/UserGroupController override it to install the\n  summary projection early when \"users\" is requested.\n- UserRole/UserGroup gain hasUserSummaries() so FieldFilterService's own\n  applyUserSummaries skips a redundant fetch if the controller hook\n  already populated it.\n\nVerified via manual instrumentation that LinkService now operates on\nthe transient summary objects (not real Hibernate entities), and via a\nGlowroot trace on a local instance with an 83,333-member role:\n\n| | Before this fix | After |\n|---|---|---|\n| Duration | ~60-90s | 2.57s |\n| SQL queries | ~230k-3 | 2 |\n\nThe wasted \"select every real User\" query (previously still firing\nonce to feed LinkService) is gone entirely. Combined with the\nDHIS2-21860 projection fix and the read-only-transaction flush guard,\nthe full round trip from the original 141s/583,335-query baseline is\nnow 2.57s/2 queries.\n\nhref does get computed on the transient summary objects, but does not\ncurrently survive into the serialized response for nested \"users.X\"\npaths -- confirmed to be a separate, pre-existing field-filter issue\nunrelated to this change (users[id] and users[*] already returned\nidentical output before any of this work, reproduced independently on\nthe 2.43.0.1 stable play instance). Tracked separately, out of scope\nhere.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"5f88670f24da82f7fb46e43e72618979330c2b8a","tree_id":"1c0e51eb761066111fa6966e46037df15a0d5c54","timestamp":"2026-07-20T18:37:47Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignees_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/assignees{/user}","blobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/git/blobs{/sha}","branches_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/branches{/branch}","co